%h2 Get more success in your daily life!
%p Todo lists have been known to help productivity and keep people from making mistakes. |
  Use this fun app to offload some of that brainpower into written form, so you can do more, better. |

%section
  %h3 Sign In
  = form_for :session, '/session' do |f|
    = f.input :email
    = f.input :password
    = f.submit 'Sign In'
 
  %p Don't have an account? #{link_to 'Registration', new_users_path} is easy
